*********************** Notice ***********************
This code has a target of Android2.2/API8
This code is tested by Galaxy tab 10.1 running Android3.0
There are some bug when running on 2.x devices.

Major problems:
1. distinguishing roll & pitch
2. setting the camera resolution by program

